# 懵然不知
(pos:成語)
<explanation>
yue:完全唔知曉，或者對某件事好模糊、搞唔清嘅狀態（量詞：個）
eng:ignorant; unaware; in a state of confusion
<eg>
yue:佢對呢個新政策懵然不知，所以唔敢亂講。 (keoi5 noi6 goi5 nei5 goi5 san1 zing3 ceung3 mong4 jan4 bat1 zai1, so1 ji5 mou5 gong2 luan2 gong2.)
eng:He was completely unaware of this new policy, so he didn't dare to speak rashly. [end of text]


